{"tid":1247150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：200萬人遊行登英兒童雜誌封面 港府巧威威 外國細路都識 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-06-21T04:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T04:15:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"281d6ce4eb9a65502a277d3b9a49057af347feed","tid":1247150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:12:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190621/20709583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F20709583&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=622fa4ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F20709583&h=484db167\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190621/20709583</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：200萬人遊行登英兒童雜誌封面<br />\n港府巧威威 外國細路都識 - 李八方<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190621/large/a1602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190621%2Flarge%2Fa1602a.gif&h=bd3803d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n香港200萬港人上街反送中惡法引起全球關注，香港秩序井然、和平嘅遊行，幾乎霸佔全球所有主流媒體封面或頭條，但估唔到今次香港人上街，連外國兒童雜誌都關心！<br />\n<br />\nThe Week Junior係英國一本畀兒童同少年睇嘅雜誌，今期佢哋就用香港200萬人上街做封面，林鄭月娥同港府唔止「揚名」國際，仲連外國細路仔同青少年都知到香港政府點將港人送中，搞到官逼民反！<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190621/large/a1602b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190621%2Flarge%2Fa1602b.gif&h=33b70434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190621/large/a1602c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190621%2Flarge%2Fa1602c.gif&h=ff1d04aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德領事館借古諷港<br />\n<br />\n講到外國勢力，又點少得成日喺fb抽港府水嘅德國駐港總領事館！今個星期日香港200萬港人上街反送中惡法後，前日佢哋喺fb出po，話66年前嘅6月17日，東德各大城鎮有差不多100萬人示威遊行，要求實施自由選舉同埋統一兩德，呢場抗爭遭當時蘇共以坦克鎮壓，估計有多達50人喪生，而為咗紀念六一七事件，西德政府自1953年開始到東西德統一，將每年6月17日定為國慶節，直到1990年先再將「德國統一日」改定於10月3日。正當香港人同樣以上街抵抗中共打壓，呢個po對香港人嚟講特別有深意。<br />\n<br />\n李八方  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (馬龍)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：醫學會反送中冇立場 蔡堅扯火 (李八方)"},{"pid":"18cd2e4f8b32cce5d1f749cfd9191dd76544e5e1","tid":1247150,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1032ab308ad9b540bd78546b8e24db106ae87055","tid":1247150,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"睇左200萬兒登仔遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}